summary.span: 封装可扩展样式表转换语言 (XSLT) 处理器的当前执行上下文，使 XML 路径语言 (XPath) 在 XPath 表达式中解析函数、参数和命名空间。

span.span: Encapsulates the current execution context of the Extensible Stylesheet Language for Transformations (XSLT) processor allowing XML Path Language (XPath) to resolve functions, parameters, and namespaces within XPath expressions.

remarks.format: ## Remarks 有关详细信息使用，请参阅文章 Q324899，"HOW TO:: 实现和使用自定义函数时你执行 XPath 查询在 Visual Basic.NET"Microsoft 知识库中在http://support.microsoft.com。For more information on using , see article Q324899, "HOW TO: Implement and Use Custom Functions When You Execute XPath Queries in Visual Basic .NET" in the Microsoft Knowledge Base at http://support.microsoft.com.

summary.span: 当在派生类中重写时，根据 XSLT 处理器加载文档的顺序对两个文档的基统一资源标识符 (URI) 进行比较（为 类）。

span.span: When overridden in a derived class, compares the base Uniform Resource Identifiers (URIs) of two documents based upon the order the documents were loaded by the XSLT processor (that is, the class).

returns.span: 说明两个基 URI 的相对顺序的整数值。如果 在 之前发生，则为 1；如果两个基 URI 同时发生，则为 0；如果 在 之后发生，则为 1。

span.span: An integer value describing the relative order of the two base URIs: -1 if occurs before ; 0 if the two base URIs are identical; and 1 if occurs after .

remarks.format: ## Remarks 此方法支持 XSLT`document()`函数，后者指定跨多个文档所选节点始终以相同的顺序返回。This method supports the XSLT `document()` function which specifies that nodes selected across multiple documents are always returned in the same order. > [!NOTE] > 顺序是特定于实现的。The order is implementation-specific.
